name: UToPX // Unknown Treasures of Person X

metadata.name: UToPX #1  'Lightbulb Moment 1'
metadata.description:
Polaroids found at Car Boot sale.

Taken by Person X, these polaroids provide a unique viewpoint of someone documenting the world around them. From real life moments to direct photos of a television screen, the motives of Person X are totally unclear.

I've owned and loved these polaroids for years, and hope that somehow Person X can appreciate the new digital lease of life his their art now has.

If we somehow exist in the art we make, Person X surely lives here forever.
